node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Garcia @MrRichardGarcia built an 8M real the time estate portfolio by turned 31, and now I'm selling it. Here's why...'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @MrRichardGarcia First, let me start off with how I built my portfolio. took the money made from working at Tesla, Google, and Facebook and bought multifamily real estate Just by doing the BRRRR method, I amassed a 6.7M portfolio.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Richard Garcia @MrRichardGarcia Then, 2020 hit, and my portfolio grew an extra 2M through appreciation. didn't do anything extra to make that. My properties didn't all of a sudden make more money. They just grew 2M in value. That's when I knew it was time to sell.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Richard Garcia know, know... Why would I sell a portfolio that is bringing in 25,000Ð month? I'm following the age-old saying of "buy low, sell high" When bought my real estate, it was at the lowest points (2011-2013) Ican't see the prices going much higher.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Garcia @MrRichardGarcia And where am money into? Crypto. investing all of my believe crypto is the future, and buying BTc at 25k/ ETH at 1.5k is an absolute steal.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Garcia @MrRichardGarcia The great thing about this is I'm transparent with all my positions and holdings. If I'm right, you'll see my net worth double in 3-5 years. If I'm wrong, you'll see me lose half of my net worth.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @MrRichardGarcia Too many people are all talk with no skin in the game on social media. At least you get to see my wins and losses. And if you catc catch me on a livestream, drop some serious game. Either way, you can stay updated with all of this by following me.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Garcia @MrRichardGarcia If you've gotten this far, just know that 8M is gross, and only 5M ofitis equity. I'm also keeping 2M in real estate just to pay for my lifestyle.'.
